===Comic book adaptation===
A single-issue [[comic book]] adaptation of ''Shinobi'' was created by [[Scott Allie]], published by [[Dark Horse Comics]], and released in 2002. The plot follows Hotsuma and other characters from the game.<ref>{{cite web|title=Shinobi #1|url=http://www.amazon.com/Shinobi-1-Dark-Horse/dp/B000IFX1RG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&s=books&qid=1271540236&sr=1-1|publisher=[[Amazon.com]]|accessdate=April 28, 2010}}</ref>

